{"title":"Societal impacts of climate change from local to global","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":""},"headingText":"Societal impacts of climate change from local to global","headingAttr":{"id":"","classes":["unlisted"],"keyvalue":[]},"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n<div style=\"padding: 2.5rem 1rem 2rem 1rem;\">\n\n<div style=\"font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.02em; margin: 0;\">\nKakinuma Lab.\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size: 1.0rem; color: #666; margin: 0.15rem 0 0 0;\">\nFrontier Research Institute for Interdisciplinary Sciences, Tohoku University\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"max-width: 820px; padding: 0 1rem; line-height: 1.85; font-size: 1.02rem;\">\n\n\nOur lab focuses on the interplay between climate and environmental change and population dynamics, examining how climate change affects human societies across multiple spatial scales. We empirically investigate its impacts on human migration, health, ecosystem vulnerability, and social inequality. Our goal is to deepen understanding of these patterns and mechanisms from local to global levels and to support the development of adaptation strategies for future climate extremes.\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 1rem;\">\n[ORCID](https://orcid.org/0000-0003-4647-9582) ·\n[Scholar](https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=aPhJA6wAAAAJ&hl=ja) ·\n[Researchmap](https://researchmap.jp/kknmk) ·\n[Instagram](https://www.instagram.com/kaoru_kaki) ·\n[Bluesky](https://bsky.app/profile/kaoru-kaki.bsky.social)\n</div>\n\n---\n\n### 気候変動の社会影響を、地域から全球まで横断的に解明する {.unlisted}\n\n本研究室では、気候・環境変化と人口動態の相互作用に着目し、気候変動が人間社会に与える影響を地域から全球までの多様な空間スケールで明らかにします。とくに、人口移動、健康、生態系の脆弱性、社会的格差への影響を実証的に検証しています。地域から全球までのパターンとメカニズムの理解を深め、気候変動適応策の検討につなげることを目標としています。\n\n</div>","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n<div style=\"padding: 2.5rem 1rem 2rem 1rem;\">\n\n<div style=\"font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.02em; margin: 0;\">\nKakinuma Lab.\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size: 1.0rem; color: #666; margin: 0.15rem 0 0 0;\">\nFrontier Research Institute for Interdisciplinary Sciences, Tohoku University\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"max-width: 820px; padding: 0 1rem; line-height: 1.85; font-size: 1.02rem;\">\n\n### Societal impacts of climate change from local to global {.unlisted}\n\nOur lab focuses on the interplay between climate and environmental change and population dynamics, examining how climate change affects human societies across multiple spatial scales. We empirically investigate its impacts on human migration, health, ecosystem vulnerability, and social inequality. Our goal is to deepen understanding of these patterns and mechanisms from local to global levels and to support the development of adaptation strategies for future climate extremes.\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 1rem;\">\n[ORCID](https://orcid.org/0000-0003-4647-9582) ·\n[Scholar](https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=aPhJA6wAAAAJ&hl=ja) ·\n[Researchmap](https://researchmap.jp/kknmk) ·\n[Instagram](https://www.instagram.com/kaoru_kaki) ·\n[Bluesky](https://bsky.app/profile/kaoru-kaki.bsky.social)\n</div>\n\n---\n\n### 気候変動の社会影響を、地域から全球まで横断的に解明する {.unlisted}\n\n本研究室では、気候・環境変化と人口動態の相互作用に着目し、気候変動が人間社会に与える影響を地域から全球までの多様な空間スケールで明らかにします。とくに、人口移動、健康、生態系の脆弱性、社会的格差への影響を実証的に検証しています。地域から全球までのパターンとメカニズムの理解を深め、気候変動適応策の検討につなげることを目標としています。\n\n</div>"},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"paged","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":false,"echo":true,"output":true,"warning":true,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"engine":"markdown"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"defau